# QR card file must stay in sync

When you change anything that affects what customers see via the demo or the QR code:

1. **Also update `qr-card.html`** in the same change (or in an immediate follow-up).

Apply updates to the QR card when you:
- Change the **demo URL** (e.g. project-demo.html path or domain) → update the QR image `src` and the link `href` in qr-card.html.
- Change **branding or tagline** that appears on the QR card (e.g. "YOU BUILD, WE PRESENT") → update the `.qr-title` text in qr-card.html.
- Change **footer or credit** text (e.g. "all right reserved to Parkook.com") → update the `.qr-footer` block in qr-card.html.
- Add or change a **landing link** (e.g. index.html or parkook.com) → update the footer link in qr-card.html if it points there.

Keep the QR card’s link and QR image URL identical to the live demo URL (currently `https://itissiamak-hub.github.io/Constructing-Landing/project-demo.html`).
